<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
  {{> head}}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://cdn.leafletjs.com/leaflet-0.7.3/leaflet.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Leaflet.awesome-markers/2.0.2/leaflet.awesome-markers.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/style.css" type="text/css" />

</head>
<body>
  {{> header}}
  {{> start}}
  <ul>
    <li>資料來源：<a href="http://data.tainan.gov.tw/">臺南市政府資料開放平台</a></li>
    <li>熱區及噴藥日期計算方式：以最新確診病例日期為基礎來計算</i>
    <li>最後更新日期：2015/9/25</i>
  <li>最新病例資料：<span class="current"><span></i>
    <li>噴藥資料：2015/8/13～2015/9/14</i>
    <li>
    相關網站：<a href="http://real.taiwanstat.com/dengue-spatial-temporal/">台南2015年即時登革熱資訊</a> | <a href="http://web.ncku.edu.tw/files/11-1000-17008.php?Lang=zh-tw">成功大學登革熱防疫專區</a> | <a href="http://nidss.cdc.gov.tw/ch/Default.aspx?op=4">傳染病統計資料查詢系統</a> | <a href="http://www.cdc.gov.tw/list.aspx?treeid=d315941f29223d38&nowtreeid=d315941f29223d38">疫病管制署登革熱專區</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="visual">
    <div class="ui form">
      <div class="inline fields">
        <label>熱區時間計算：</label>
        <div class="field">
          <div class="ui radio checkbox">
            <input type="radio" name="days" value="3" checked="checked">
            <label>3天內</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <div class="ui radio checkbox">
            <input type="radio" name="days" value="5">
            <label>5天內<span class="browser-note">（建議以Chrome、Firefox顯示）</span></label>
          </div>
        </div> 
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ui toggle checkbox">
      <input type="checkbox" name="drug" value="drug" checked="checked">
      <label>顯示7天內噴藥區域（50公尺）</label>
    </div>
      <span class="date">日期：<span class="current"></span></span>
    <div id="map"> </div>
    <div class="ui slider range" style="width:100%">
      <input type="range"
      min="0" max="240" value="0" tabindex="0"/>
      <span class="ui icon buttons">
      <button class="ui button stepback">
          <i class="step backward icon"></i>
      </button>
      <button class="ui button play">
        <i class="play icon"></i>
      </button>
      <button class="ui button pause">
        <i class="pause icon"></i>
      </button>
      </span> 
    </div>
    <div id="bar">
    </div>
  </div>
  {{> end}}
   <script src="https://cdn.firebase.com/js/client/2.2.9/firebase.js"></script>
   <script src="http://cdn.leafletjs.com/leaflet-0.7.3/leaflet.js"></script>
   <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Leaflet.awesome-markers/2.0.2/leaflet.awesome-markers.min.js"></script>
   <script src="http://labratrevenge.com/d3-tip/javascripts/d3.tip.v0.6.3.js"></script>
   <script type="text/javascript" src="./js/index.js" charset="UTF-8"> </script>
   <script type="text/javascript" src="./js/bar.js" charset="UTF-8"> </script>
    <!-- my js & css -->
  {{> footer}}
</body>
